author: Aric Jenkins
description: Greg Gianforte was charged with misdemeanor assault
title: Reporter Claims Montana GOP House Candidate Greg Gianforte 'Body Slammed' Him

author: BBC News
description: Montana candidate Greg Gianforte faces a misdemeanour charge over a clash with a Guardian journalist.
title: US Republican Greg Gianforte charged over Guardian reporter 'body slam'

author: Alex Johnson
description: Republican Greg Gianforte won Montana's special election a day after he was charged with assault for allegedly body-slamming a reporter.
title: Republican Greg Gianforte, charged with assault on reporter, wins Montana special election

author: Adam Shaw
description: Republican Greg Gianforte won Thursday's special election for the U.S. House in Montana, defeating the Democrats -- and the media.
title: Greg Gianforte Stuns Media, Democrats in Montana House Win

author: Alicia Shepard
description: Donald Trump made the media the "enemy of the people" during his campaign. Greg Gianforte body slammed a Guardian journalist last night, reminding us how important our First Amendment is.
title: Greg Gianforte's assault on a journalist is an assault on all Americans

author: Jethro Mullen
description: The alleged assault of Guardian reporter Ben Jacobs by Republican congressional candidate Greg Gianforte set social media alight on Wednesday night.
title: Twitter erupts over GOP candidate Greg Gianforte's alleged assault on reporter

author: Matthew Yglesias
description: Greg Gianforte won a narrow victory in Montana, a safe red seat. That is a bad sign for Republicans, Matt Yglesias writes in Vox.
title: Op-Ed: Why Greg Gianforte's win in Montana election is great news ... for Democrats

author: Lauren Fox, CNN
description: Republican Greg Gianforte has won the special election for Montana's open US House seat, CNN projects, defeating Democrat Rob Quist and capping off a whirlwind final 36 hours of the campaign that saw Gianforte being charged for allegedly assaulting a reporter.
title: Republican Greg Gianforte wins Montana special election, CNN projects

author: Spiegel Online
description: Der Republikaner Greg Gianforte soll einen Reporter des "Guardian" zu Boden geworfen und seine Brille zerstört zu haben. Spitzenpolitiker Paul Ryan steht dennoch zu ihm.
title: Greg Gianforte: Mutmaßliche Prügelattacke - Republikaner halten an Parteifreund fest

author: Janet Hook
description: Republican Greg Gianforte won a hotly contested House race in Montana, holding on to a GOP seat despite an 11th-hour charge of assaulting a reporter.
title: Republican Greg Gianforte Wins Montana House Special Election Despite Assault Charge
